a.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A Retina-Ready Responsive Creative WordPress Theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/impreza-retina-responsive-wordpress-theme/6434280/\">Purchase Impreza theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Black Studio TinyMCE Widget plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/black-studio-tinymce-widget/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/blackstudio.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin adds a new Visual Editor widget type that allows you to insert rich text and media objects in your sidebars with no hassle.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/black-studio-tinymce-widget/\">Download Black Studio TinyMCE Widget plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WP Membership plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/wp-membership/10066554\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/membership.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>WP Membership plugin Perfect for newsletters, premium content sites, etc&#8230;\n</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/wp-membership/10066554\">Purchase WP Membership plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=O18gqI9PtTc:ruEADnq153w:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=O18gqI9PtTc:ruEADnq153w:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=O18gqI9PtTc:ruEADnq153w:gIN9vFwOqvQ